General.Name: Iodm Ltd
General.Description: IODM Limited provides cloud based software as a service in Australia, New Zealand, and the United Kingdom. It develops an automated debtor management solution that offers accounts receivable monitoring and collection management tool through a central cloud based platform for businesses. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
